Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.98,KazuyaShuuSign,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.71,0:00:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toate avem peste 20 de ani!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.46,0:00:09.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Vom ajunge imediat în ultima stație: Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.27,0:00:12.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Vă rugăm să aveți grijă la coborâre.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:15.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aici voi locui de azi înainte.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sper să întâlnesc niște oameni drăguți.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.57,0:00:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deci aceasta este Stația Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:39.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arată exact ca la televizor!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:42.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vai, ce de oameni.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.78,0:00:45.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ei bine, deci trebuie doar să schimb trenurile la...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:46.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aș face bine să nu iau trenul greșit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:47.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:50.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U-Un hoț!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.73,0:00:56.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cum îndrăznești să iei lucrurile altei persoane?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.36,0:00:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poftim. Ești bine?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:01.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O, îți mulțumesc foarte mult.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:08.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este așa de frumoasă...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are acel aspect metropolitan rafinat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.32,0:01:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Așa frumoasă și grozavă și...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:16.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai grijă, bine?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:19.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îți mulțumesc foarte, foarte mult!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.28,0:01:21.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,La revedere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.03,0:01:26.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Presupun că există persoane \Ndrăguțe în Tokyo, la urma urmei.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:32.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tată, mamă, cred că voi fi bine aici!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.19,0:01:42.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vă mulțumim că ați mers cu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:52.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unde sunt...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:58.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tată, mamă, nu cred că voi fi bine aici deloc...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.73,0:02:01.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am reușit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:04.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mă bucur că am luat trenul \Nshinkansen de mai devreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:07.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă aș fi întârziat...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:10.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}Femeie necioplită și nepricepută de la țară!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:11.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O, nu! O femeie demonică din Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:13.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mersi că m-ai așteptat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:15.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu! Îmi cer scuze! Îmi cer scuze că am venit în Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:17.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mă aștepți de mult timp?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:18.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:22.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tu ești Amatsuki Michiru, nu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.44,0:02:24.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Da.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:27.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu sunt Midorikawa Kae. Am venit ca să te conduc!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:31.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu sunt Amatsuki! Încântată de cunoștință!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.57,0:02:34.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Deci... Așa arată o femeie din Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:36.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mergem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:37.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.61,0:02:40.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Trebuie să dau tot ce pot...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.61,0:02:41.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uau!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:44.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aceasta este Stella House Haruno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:46.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deci asta este noua mea casă!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:48.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este o casă cu chirie numai pentru femei.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suntem deja trei care locuiesc aici.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:53.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iar tu ești a patra, Michiru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:56.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vai, devin agitată acum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.23,0:03:00.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Scuzați deranjul...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.69,0:03:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,De azi înainte, asta este și casa ta, deci nu trebuie să fii timidă.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:06.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O, ai dreptate...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Am ajuns.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:11.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bine ai venit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:14.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Asta este foarte jenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:18.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nao-chan, noua noastră colegă de cameră a ajuns!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:23.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vai, nu fi așa gălăgioasă...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:26.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haide, ridică-te.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eu sunt Kiriyama Nao.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.65,0:03:33.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mă bucur să te cunosc...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:36.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îmi cer scuze pentru asta, Michiru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:38.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's been drinking since noon\Nsince she has the day off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:41.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,New roommate?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:42.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:46.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Stella House!\NWe've been looking forward to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:51.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now to celebrate! By cracking open a Yebisu beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:53.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, you're really going to keep drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, duh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're talking about Yebisu here. Yebisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:04:00.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was worried you'd have downed them all already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:03.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I would never!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:04.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:05.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:07.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why are there two missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll wash the dishes to make up for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now as way of apology allow me to pour you\Na fan-freaking-tastic glass of Yebisu beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold that glass for me, would ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,L-like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:22.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:24.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here GOES!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:29.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Relax, relax! A good pouring is key!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.69,0:04:32.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First we fill it up about half way and then STOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now we let the fizz there settle down\Nand wait until it's about half foam half beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:45.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next we pour very carefully making sure\Nto keep the foam until it's about 90% full.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you gotta hold back that desire\Nto gulp it down and just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:52.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now here's the last part!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pour the rest in nice and slow\Nto bring the head to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:05:01.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The perfect ratio is 7 to 3 and with that it's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:05.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my! It's like something out of a commercial!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:06.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:10.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the ideal way to pour\Nthe perfect glass of Yebisu beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I call it the three step pour!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:16.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now then, let's celebrate Michiru Amatsuki\Nmoving in with us here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:17.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:23.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The foam is so fluffy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:25.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.11,0:05:29.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The foam is so fine and the bubbles have settled down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the magic of the three step pour!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:34.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now Michiru-chan, make sure you eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.82,0:05:37.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chilled tofu is the perfect match for a summer drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:41.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I topped it off with some plum and okra\Nto make it even more refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't mind if I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:47.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that plum accent really stimulates the palate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:49.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it looks just as wonderful as it tastes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:52.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And nothing like some beer to wash it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can she drink that much...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.78,0:05:57.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's some chopped avocado and tuna\Ndressed with wasabi soy sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:06:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The avocado is so rich it's just perfect with a beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:05.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That wasabi is just the perfect dose of spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:08.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Small dishes like these are what summer is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:10.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The heat can drain your appetite after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:12.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can she eat that much...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:17.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you've got your chopsticks\Nwarmed up and ready, it's time for our main dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shrimp and summer veggie tempura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:21.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bring on the fried goodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even in this heat you can't help\Nbut crave something deep fried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:28.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:32.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Woah, hang in there Kae!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:34.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll crank up the A/C!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:42.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now nice and hot tempura is fine with salt. But here we\Ndig in with some grated daikon and dipping sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:47.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my! How refreshing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:49.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Glad to have you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.11,0:06:56.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that grated daikon is to die for!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.67,0:06:59.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that freshly fried batter is so light and crispy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fried food and beer go hand in hand, but a premium\Nbeer like this would be wasted on anything too heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:07.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess there's food to match every sort of drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:14.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be honest though Yebisu beer\Ntastes great no matter what you eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:16.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How uncouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:20.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, by the way, why did you\Nmove out to Tokyo anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:24.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For work! I'm going to be working\Nsales a startup company.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:28.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to stride through the crowds in my suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:31.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Drink a smoothie every morning.\NEat my own handmade lunch in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And finish off the night at a fancy restaurant with a view!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sales sounds pretty tough, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:39.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't let your quotas drive you crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you not crush my dreams right from the get go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:44.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do both of you do, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:46.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I work in the apparel industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a wedding planner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:51.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow! Those both sounds so lovely and fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.94,0:07:55.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay what's with the silent treatment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:59.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've still got that light of hope... huh, Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were like that too, once upon a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:06.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true! We had hopes and dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:15.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,before we knew it our dreams were shattered,\Nand the hope drained form our eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:17.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before long, all we were doing\Nwas griping and moaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:21.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We want nothing but happiness,\Nbut are not spared even the time to seek it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N..Nao-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:24.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's life, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:25.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's seriously crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:28.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then one day while I was trying\Nto drown my sorrows away...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:30.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yebisu is so GOOOOD!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:32.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grant me your attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:35.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:38.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The label on that bottle you're holding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:40.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yebisu-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:44.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yebisu-sama spoke to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:46.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you poor soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:48.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that very same bottle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:51.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...is right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:54.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My lucky Yebisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:56.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This little bottle saved you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:58.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me like I'm crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:00.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and compare it to this can here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:05.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! There's a fish in the basket on this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly! It's a super rare special label!\NThe luckiest Yebisu around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nao-chan you still had that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my most cherished possession!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so yeah, that brought\Na spark of happiness back into my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.73,0:09:22.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you just do your best, okay Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:24.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lucky Yebisu here, is watching over you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:27.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm already quite lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:30.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My first time in Tokyo and I meet such friendly people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything about Tokyo is so unfamiliar, and I was\Nafraid to live alone so I picked this share house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:46.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that meant I'd have to live with people I've never\Neven met, so I was worried maybe we wouldn't get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like I was worried for nothing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:52.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So thank you both again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:56.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Michiru!\NNo, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:09:59.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.07,0:10:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! She's back! My sweet sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:07.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is our other roommate...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:10.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yup! She's Nao's little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:11.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:16.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome home! Nghh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:22.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You big meanie! Why would you avoid me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:24.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You reek of beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:27.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U-umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Michiru Amatsuki,\Nthe one you helped at Tokyo Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:33.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:34.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:38.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, nice to meet you for real though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:42.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:47.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, now! Why don't you treat me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:50.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well Makoto-chan is not exactly fond of drunks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:51.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:54.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Michiru you and Makoto know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:55.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I ran into her at Tokyo Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:59.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so lucky, she really saved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:05.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope we get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:12.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nao-chan, how long are you going\Nto sit there zoning out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:15.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, we were up so late drinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope Michiru-chan is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:20.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went and picked up breakfast at the convenience store!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:26.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is she so lively...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right? You don't feel hungover or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:31.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:34.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My parents are pretty heavy drinkers you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since I turned 20\NI've drank at home plenty with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:43.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll pick up something for us to drink\Non the way home tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:47.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, is she a heavier drinker than us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:52.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the start of my new life in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:54.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make the very best\Nof my work and home life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:12:02.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought that jingle that plays\Nat Ebisu station sounded familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:05.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Turns out it was from the Yebisu Beer commercial!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:09.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apparently it's the theme song\Nfrom the movie "The Third Man."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:12.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokyo is just so stylish!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:14.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's to another night! Cheers!
